videos.description: Campbell's Cedric Frazier trips on his way to the end zone to potentially tie the game, and following a touchdown on that drive, the Fighting Camels' 2-point conversion for the win is airmailed by Hajj-Malik Williams.
videos.headline: Campbell vs. Georgia Southern ending takes wild turn of events
